This obsoletes IRM 4.24.7, Excise Embedded Quality Review System (EQRS) and Excise National Quality Review System (NQRS). SB/SE examination quality is now aligned with the Office of Exam Quality and Technical Support (EQ&TS). On June 8, 2017, ownership of IRM 4.8.3, Technical Services, Examination Quality Measurement Staff (EQMS), was formally transferred to EQ&TS from Exam Technical Support. New IRM 4.2.8, Guidelines for SB/SE National Quality Review, and new IRM 4.24.6, Excise Tax, Technical Guidance and Information Processing for Excise Tax Examination Issues, incorporate all relevant procedural guidance from IRM 4.24.7.
Relevant content from IRM 4.24.7 moved to IRM 4.2.8 and IRM 4.24.6 as shown in the table below:
